#### Project Overview
This project analyzes Adidas sales data using SQL to uncover insights into sales performance, retailer contributions, product trends, regional performance, and profitability.

The goal is to transform raw sales data into actionable business insights that can support strategic decision-making and improve overall sales performance.

#### Objectives
- Analyze overall sales performance
- Identify top-performing retailers
- Evaluate product performance
- Compare sales across regions
- Measure profitability and operating margins
- Discover sales trends and patterns
